data.description: Experience the charm and elegance of this stunningly updated ranch-style home! Featuring three generously sized bedrooms and two full baths, this residence is a perfect blend of style and comfort. The kitchen is a chef's dream, showcasing granite countertops, a spacious island, tasteful backsplash, and modern fixtures that add a touch of luxury. The stainless steel appliances complete the contemporary look. Both bathrooms have been modernized for a fresh and sophisticated feel. Throughout the home, you'll find beautiful new laminate flooring that complements the home's aesthetic, along with ceiling fans for added comfort. The large bonus room offers versatile space for various needs. Relax on the inviting rocking chair porch or the covered patio, perfect for enjoying the serene surroundings. Nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this property is conveniently located just minutes from the Mall of Georgia, Highway 316, and I-85, providing easy access to all amenities. This home is truly a must-see for those seeking convenience and style.
